OL,6,FBy ITV News Social Affairs
OL,7,FCorrespondent Sarah Corker and Senior
OL,8,FProducer Lottie Kilraine
OL,10,FSurvivors of Britain's forced forced
OL,11,Fadoption scandal have gathered in
OL,12,FCumbria to remember children who died
OL,13,Fin church run institutions and were
OL,14,Fburied in mass unmarked graves.
OL,16,FIt comes after an ITV News
OL,17,Finvestigation last year discovered
OL,18,Fthat 45 babies had died at a former
OL,19,FChurch of England home for unmarried
OL,20,Fmothers and were buried in secret in a
OL,21,Fmass unmarked grave in Kendal.
