OL,6,FIf you or anyone you know has been
OL,7,Faffected by this issue or has a story
OL,8,Fto share, you can get in touch by
OL,9,Femailing: socialaffairs@itv.com
OL,11,FSt Monica's in Kendal was run by the
OL,12,FDiocese of Carlisle from 1917 until
OL,13,Fits closure in 1970.
OL,15,FStephen Hindley, who has been
OL,16,Fcampaigning for justice for nearly two
OL,17,Fdecades for his wife Judith and her
OL,18,Fson, also called Stephen, said the
OL,19,Fmemorial has given them "the dignity
OL,20,Fthey so richly deserve".
