OL,6,FStephen was born in 1964 with
OL,7,Fdisabilities, but he was "cruelly
OL,8,Fdenied proper medical care and died 11
OL,9,Fweeks later", Mr Hindley said.
OL,11,FJudith never recovered from that
OL,12,Ftrauma and in 2006 took her own life
OL,13,Fclose to the cemetery where her baby
OL,14,Fis buried.
OL,16,FLast year, an ITV News investigation
OL,17,Ffound there are hundreds of mass
OL,18,Funmarked graves of babies in
OL,19,Fcemeteries across England, from
OL,20,FNewcastle to Hampshire.
