OL,6,FPregnant and unmarried, Norah, who was
OL,7,Ffrom Barrow-in-Furness, was sent away
OL,8,Fto St Monica's in Kendal where she was
OL,9,Flater told that her baby daughter
OL,10,FFaith had been stillborn.
OL,12,FBurial records seen by ITV News
OL,13,Fsuggest that Norah was lied to and
OL,14,Fshow that Faith had lived for 12 hours
OL,15,Fand was buried without the family's
OL,16,Fknowledge in a mass grave in Kendal.
OL,18,FMr Chubb said Friday's memorial was an
OL,19,F"important recognition that Faith
OL,20,Fexisted".
